Kanjalo, ipenseli yaba umhlobo wabantu abaninzi entle xa kuvela.
Ngokudabukisayo, njengoko iindlela zokubhala ezintsha zivelile, ipenseli inikwe imeko kunye nomsebenzi ophansana.
Abantu ngoku babhala imiyalezo kwiikrini zekhompyutha, banokudingi ukusondela kumatshini wokucija amapensela.
Umntu unokuzibuza ukuba kuya kwenzeka ntoni ngekhibhodi xa kufika into entsha.
Uphononongo lwamashumi amabini anesihlanu leminyaka lubonise ukuba kukho iindidi ezimbini zokuhluka: ezifihliweyo kunye nokuveziwe.
Ukuguquka kwenza ukuhluka kwezakhi zofuzo ezintsha, kwaye ukukhetha kuzisusa kwimenyu eveziweyo.
Ukwahluka kokwahlulwa kunye nokuhlanganiswa kwehla kwenyuke phakathi kwezigaba ezimbli kwisizukulwana ngasinye.
